creator: Joyo Health
descriptionHtml:
Who is Joyo Health meant for?

Joyo health is a one stop solution for people who are battling with sexual health issues like premature ejaculation, erectile dysfunction, low libido, low sex drive, nightfall, masturabtion addiction, sexual phobia like vaginismus, female orgasm problem and mental health issues which includes anxiety, stress, depression, insomnia, OCD, alcohol addiction, PTSD and memeory issues.

Joyo Health provides a platform where you can connect with people having similar problems which you are facing and at the same time listen to you without any judgement under the supervision of our experts which includes psychologists, psychiatrists, urologist and Gynaecologist. At Joyo Health, you can be anonymous & express your problems without any fear of being judged. Joyo Health is for everyone who needs support & talking about your troubles is often seen as the first step of therapy. Talking about your problems will help you fight off your sexual and mental health issues.

There are times when you are struggling but don’t know what to do and whom to approach and given the delicate nature of the problem, can’t express ourselves in front of our closed ones. These situations can be sexual or mental in nature. Sexual conditions includes - Early Ejaculation, Erectile Dysfunction, Low sex desire, Orgasm problem, Sex Phobia, Female sex Problems, Relationship issues, Masturbation, Vaginusmus. On the other hand mental health conditions will be - Stress, Anxiety, Depression, Sleep Disorder, OCD, Memory Loss, Addiction, Panic disorder, Eating Disorder and PTSD. In situations like these a community where you can connect with people who have faced or are currently facing similar issues can give your morale a boost. On top of this, a little guidance from our experts on mental and sexual health topics can give you a right direction on how to approach any problem.

At Joyo Health, we firmly believe that guidance should only come from mental health experts who are qualified to provide therapy & peer support from those who have crossed this difficult path before; hence, our endeavour at bringing peers with similar experiences together. Joyo Health is a safe space where you can talk about anything anonymously related to mental health be it Stress, Anxiety, Depression, Sleep Disorder, OCD, Memory Loss, Addiction, Panic disorder, Eating Disorder, PTSD or sexual health which includes Early Ejaculation, Erectile Dysfunction, Low sex desire, Orgasm problem, Sex Phobia, Sexual health, Female sex Problems, Relationship issues, Masturbation, Nightfall.


Features of Joyo Health

100% Safe Place - Spamming & trolling of content is strictly prohibited. We incline to take strict actions against such behaviours.

Peer support - Our anonymous community is built to support each other during tough times & help in building self confidence.

Expert Guidance - At Joyo, you can always seek advice from our experts for free on topics such as premature ejaculation, erectile dysfunction, Low libido, Low sex drive, nightfall, depression, PTSD, stress, anxiety, OCD, sleep issues, low self-esteem, Intimacy and other mental health problems without any charges. We believe in good sexual & mental wellbeing for everyone.

Anonymous Community- You’ll get peer support for PME, ED, Low Sexual Drive, Increase Sexual timings, Stress, Anxiety, Depression, Relationship issues, Sleep and other mental health problems without revealing your identity.
